1. *Tada* je zaista bilo svega po malo. (At that time there was really a bit of everything.)
2. Kada je *tada* čuo za to, bio je šokiran. (When he heard about it then, he was shocked.)
3. *Tad* se nije sviđalo njegovo ponašanje. (At that time his behavior wasn't liked.)
4. *Tadu* niko nije mogao da predvidi. (Nobody could predict that at that time.)
5. *Tade* je bilo izazova. (At that time there were challenges.)